estimated_minutes: 150
acceptance_criteria: "pm notes/learnings support --edit <index> and --delete <index> with 1-based indexing, history ops, and ownership/audit-bypass semantics identical to comments; input sources aligned (--stdin/--file or documented '--add -' everywhere consistently); contracts + MCP schema + completion + docs updated per the new-command-wiring checklist; regression tests for edit/delete on both facets"
