  src/cli/commands/comments.ts,project,"reference implementation: edit/delete + stdin/file input sources"
  src/cli/commands/learnings.ts,project,needs edit/delete parity
  src/cli/commands/notes.ts,project,needs edit/delete parity
body: "## Context\nAnnotation facets share runAnnotationCommand (src/cli/commands/annotation-command.ts) but only comments.ts wires edit/delete and multiple input sources. notes.ts and learnings.ts expose add-only. Any mistaken note/learning (e.g. the pm-vcu7 flag-swallow) is permanent via the CLI; fixing it needs manual storage surgery plus history re-anchor, which no agent should do.\n\n## Approach\nExtend the shared annotation-command machinery so edit/delete are facet-generic (comments' implementation likely already is); wire the options in notes.ts/learnings.ts; align input-source flags. Coordinate with pm-yql1 (facet grammar consolidation) so the unified facet noun exposes the same verbs — implementing this first gives yql1 a uniform surface to consolidate.\n\n## Definition of done\nBad entries on any annotation facet are correctable with pm CLI only, with history recorded."
